2003-09-10  Kevin Buettner  <kevinb@redhat.com>

	From Jimi Xenidis  <jimix@watson.ibm.com>:
	* linux-target.c (reginfo): The MQ register is for IBM POWER
	(pre-PowerPC) architecture, and is undefined in PPC GNU/Linux
	environment.

